1. [done]in the flag_map (bitmap[id + MAP_SIZE]), one byte for all blocks, one byte for the current blocks
    current blocks: bitmap[id + MAP_SIZE] &= 254; //1111 1110
    all blocks: bitmap[id + MAP_SIZE] &= 253; //1111 1101
    crasher blocks: bitmap[id + MAP_SIZE] &= 251; //1111 1011

2. [done]for crasher: after tracer runs, update the information of crasher blocks
    if ((bitmap[id + MAP_SIZE] & 1) == 0)  // current covered blocks
                bitmap[id + MAP_SIZE] &= 251;  // all covered crash blocks

3. [done]read and write [flag_id, inst_begin, inst_end, block_addr]

4. [done]add crasher in untracer_dyn.c
    update crasher.all